      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING HOULIHAN (2) got around 520m in a fast 29.82 when winning a Grade 5 at Q Parklands last start. Rates a top chance again if runs up to latest. SANDAVE STAPLES (1) is worth forgiving for her last effort when fourth (16.79) at this track over 300m. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Has a strong record from box 1, including two wins. Should be about the mark. ZIPPING MEHARY (7) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 3 lengths at Q Parklands in a handy 29.87 beating Terra Bella. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Should be in this for a long way. LITTLE ROWDY (8) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot from this box most recently.",
